  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dbd\u0dba \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0db6\u0ddd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dd3 13 \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A 13-year-old student died after getting stuck in a water-filled culvert",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kurunegala Police say that a 13-year-old school student has died after falling into a water-filled culvert due to the torrential rain that fell in the Kurunegala area today (05).",
        "Sachitra Senaratne, a resident of Kurunegala Jayantipura area, who was studying in the ninth year of Kurunegala Maliadeva Adarsh \u200b\u200bMaha Vidyalaya, was involved in the accident. He had met with this accident near his residence.",
        "The police say that he met with this accident yesterday afternoon while he was traveling on a side road leading to Jayanthipura area to go home after finishing school.",
        "It is said that he slipped on the side of the road to give way to a van transporting students from Kurunegala Bandaranaike Vidyalaya and fell into the canal. He was swept away in the waterway and stuck in the culvert.",
        "Heavy rain fell continuously in the Kurunegala area and due to this, the canal flowing on that road has overflowed and water has flowed. Due to this, it is said that the surrounding area including the road was completely covered with water.",
        "Later, Kurunegala Police and the soldiers of the nearby Vahera Army Camp used a backhoe to dismantle the culvert and after an hour of great effort, the student who was stuck in the culvert was freed and admitted to the Kurunegala Teaching Hospital Emergency Treatment Center for treatment.",
        "The staff of the intensive care unit of the Kurunegala Teaching Hospital have worked hard to save the life of the student who is in danger."
      ],
